509
00:56:47,137 --> 00:56:49,765
- Brian.
- Hey, hand me a beer, will you?

510
00:57:06,657 --> 00:57:07,988
Warm beer.

511
00:57:09,793 --> 00:57:11,420
Tastes like piss.

512
00:57:21,872 --> 00:57:23,806
- What are we gonna do?
- I don't know.

513
00:57:23,874 --> 00:57:26,172
